longBusinessSummary: Kinbasha Gaming International, Inc. owns and operates retail gaming centers in Japan. The company operates pachinko parlors that offer customers to play the pachinko and pachislo games. The company was founded in 1954 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, Nevada.
